<TI>

<s docid="FBIS3-45658" num="7"> Tenders Opened for Main Part of Three Gorges Dam</s>
</TI>
</H3>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-45658" num="8"> OW1501135394 Beijing XINHUA in English 1317 GMT 15 Jan 94</s>
</F>
<F>

<s docid="FBIS3-45658" num="9"> OW1501135394</s>
</F>
