<s docid="FBIS4-47629" num="305"> Foreign Trade and Investment - Foreign-Funded Holding Companies Seen As Rising Trend -- Despite the lack of clear rules governing their operations, China is seeing growing interest among foreign investors in the use of umbrella companies to oversee rapidly expanding businesses.</s>

