<s docid="FBIS4-47629" num="732"> (Tokyo NIKKEI KINYU SHIMBUN 26 Apr 94 p 1) Resolution Highlights City's Growth, Development Objectives -- At its midterm party conference held on 28-31 March, the Ho Chi Minh City party organization endorsed a resolution containing the following major economic objectives: 1.</s>

